" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Leica_S2\" title=\"Leica S2\">Leica S2</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Leica_S_(Typ_006)\" title=\"Leica S (Typ 006)\">Leica S (Typ 006)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Leica_S_(Typ_007)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Leica S (Typ 007) (page does not exist)\">Leica S (Typ 007)</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">L mount (Autofocus MILC) series</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Leica_T_(Typ_701)\" title=\"Leica T (Typ 701)\">Leica T (Typ 701)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Leica_TL\" title=\"Leica TL\">Leica TL</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Leica_TL2\" title=\"Leica TL2\">Leica TL2</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Leica_CL_(2017)\" title=\"Leica CL (2017)\">Leica CL (2017)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Leica_SL_(Typ_601)\" title=\"Leica SL (Typ 601)\">Leica SL (Typ 601)</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Digital compact camera series</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Leica_X1\" title=\"Leica X1\">Leica X1</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Leica_X2\" title=\"Leica X2\">Leica X2</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Leica_X_Vario\" title=\"Leica X Vario\">Leica X Vario</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Leica_X_(Typ_113)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Leica X (Typ 113)\">Leica X</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Leica_Q\" title=\"Leica Q\">Leica Q</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Digilux (digital) s